@Deprecated(forRemoval=true) public class JDOQLResultQueryParams<T extends PersistableObject,​Q extends javax.jdo.query.PersistableExpression<T>> extends JDOParameters<T,​Q,​JDOQLResultQueryParams<T,​Q>>
Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
This class is designed to construct/detail JDOQLTypedQuery to select list of list. Each list item contains values of fields taken from stored objects.
